 consequence that the applicant contends for.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\qj{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang2057\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057 
