plication where the AHF complainants clearly felt they were being excluded from the negotiations and settlement only to have them thrust in their faces when they showed a determination to pursue their complaint.}}}
{\*\cs20\cf0{\*\updnprop5801}\up10\rtlch\af5\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af5\langfe255\hich\f1\fs24\lang7177\loch\f1\fs24\lang7177 }  On our interpretation this would not arise because the settlement would have had to occur during the time that the Commission retained its prerogative to prosecute.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1{\*\hyphen2\hyphlead2\hyphtrail2\hyphmax0}\ql\rtlch\af4\afs24\lang1025\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang2057\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057 
